snippet.title: Early Look:  Precipice
snippet.description:
A six-minute look at the gameplay of Precipice, made in Godot 3.1.  Spies will be deployed, countries will be invaded, nukes will be launched.

Precipice will be launching for PC, Mac, Linux, probably Android too.  English, French, German, Spanish, Russian and any other languages that we can figure out how to translate to.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/951670/Precipice/
